# Security headers (Lighthouse "Best Practices"). Cache headers live in netlify.toml.
# No Content-Security-Policy: a correct policy for the LeadConnector form, the
# *.lovable.app visualizer, Google Maps, and the inline JSON-LD/hydration scripts
# is high-maintenance and easily breaks those embeds. X-Frame-Options already
# satisfies Lighthouse's clickjacking check.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
